column2: This monthly table replaces 18-10-0030 which has been archived. This table contains monthly data starting from January 1956.
On July 17, 2018, additional historical data are available for select series upon request.
On November 30, 2020, additional series are available upon request.
On February 28, 2022, select 6- and 7-digit North American Product Classification System (NAPCS) indexes have been added to this table. Additional series continue to be available upon request.
